# Carbon Design System (ESTI)

**Canonical playbook:** [`.carbon-kit/knowledge/AGENT-RULES.md`](../../.carbon-kit/knowledge/AGENT-RULES.md)

Before editing any matched file, complete the bootstrap in that document. Do not guess Carbon APIs or invent patterns.

## Quick bootstrap

```bash
pnpm carbon:search <component|pattern>
pnpm carbon:index
```

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `.carbon-kit/knowledge/AGENT-RULES.md` | Full agent workflow |
| `.carbon-kit/knowledge/implementation_rules.md` | 20 non-negotiable rules |
| `.carbon-kit/knowledge/index.json` | Carbon doc URLs + tabs |
| `.carbon-kit/pattern-library/` | Screen patterns before code |
| `docs/esti/CARBON-UI-DIRECTION.md` | ESTI-specific exceptions |

## Validate

`pnpm --filter @esti/frontend lint` (includes `check-carbon.mjs`)
